      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW WINKWORTH (8) has a strong record here with five wins and four placings from 13 starts. Was out of placings last time (30.66) at The Meadows in a Free For All, finishing eighth and beaten 13 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. PAW FABLE (1) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 460m behind Mepunga Brockie (26.40) in a Grade 5 H. One of the better hopes. RETALIATION (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by a neck at Warragul in a handy 25.95 beating Short Straw Trev. Jumping from the pinch draw but likes the trip. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Bold showing expected again. SLICK FELIX (7) generally performs well from this box.",
